data.description: Price adjustment! Welcome to your dream home. This beautiful single-story single-family home offers an incredible blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury living. Situated on a tranquil and quiet street, this property boasts an array of remarkable features that will make you fall in love at first sight. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the spacious open floor plan. The living room flows into the dining area and kitchen, creating an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The abundance of natural light creates a warm, welcoming atmosphere. Step outside to your backyard oasis, where you'll find a private pool perfect for cooling off on those warm Tampa days. Beyond the pool, the property backs onto a conservation area, providing you with a serene and peaceful backdrop   One of the standout features of this property is the access to an extraordinary range of amenities available for a mere $40 a year grants you membership to a fantastic clubhouse, a golf course, and a delightful restaurant, access to a resort-style pool complete with a water slide and a kid-friendly splash pad. Enjoy the newly renovated state-of-the-art fitness facility basketball court and tennis court.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a single-family home with a private pool, conservation views, and access to remarkable amenities. Schedule a showing today and make this your forever home. Experience the joys of Florida living at its finest.
